Nollywood actress Uche Ogbodo received a lot of backlash over an Instagram comment she made about Judith. A post on Judith Austin’s Facebook page stated her belief that she would not be frightened to face the consequences of her relationship with Yul, as Jesus had redeemed her.
Judy Austin is one of the most beautiful actresses in Nollywood and producer of two Nollywood most loved movies.For her performance in “Native Girl,” the actress, producer, director, and company owner is well-known.
Thou many celebrities have condemned the act of taking a second wife by Yul while some encouraged his action, saying that it is better than having her as a babymama.
“I am not ashamed to say I am nothing without you Jesus. Have a lovely day bunnies” Judith posted.
“My girl”, was what Uche Ogbodo posted that got many social media users angry.


